title: NFC Eastern Promises
description:
The division previews are...back. Mina and Ben Solak of The Draft Network assess the outlook for the teams in the NFC East. Will Daniel Jones have enough time to throw to his new skill players (4:40)? Can Washington repeat as division champs if they get average QB play (21:16)? Will Dallas' defense be able to stop anyone (41:29)? And are the Eagles kind of fun (54:59)?
